					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3489662); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3489662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251150" alt="mayoculpa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3489662)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3489662); return false;" >mayoculpa</a></span> <span class="odate time_1546623055 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">04 Jan 2019 17:30</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4108410">
									

<p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2048131); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2048131&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546640219" alt="Proasek" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2048131)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/proasek" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2048131); return false;">Proasek</a></span> for inventing the Ambrose franchise, without which this horrible idea would never have evolved! Be sure to check out Proasek's <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/krona-midaeus-personnel-file">author page</a> for more ambrosial goodness.</p>
<p>Big big thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546640219" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span> for a) creating <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ambrose-london-prix-fixe">Ambrose London Prix Fixe</a> from which most of my CSS is stolen, b) helping me make the stolen code actually work, and c) giving me good crits on the text. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546640219" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for further help with CSS shenanigans. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546640219" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;">psul</a></span> on the forums and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546640219" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span> in chat for giving me excellent guidance and critiques on the text.</p>
<p>In the mainline canon, falling under the sway of a Neo-Sarkic practitioner is close to a worst case scenario.<br />
In <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/end-of-death-hub">End of Death</a> it's <em>significantly better than the default</em>.</p>
<p>An up-and-coming Neo-Sarkic empire trying to entice potential noble immigrants and extradimensional tourists would need a fancy restaurant &#8212; one which lived up to the demanding and unusual tastes of their clientele. And Ambrose would be up to the challenge.</p>
<p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Illustrated_and_descriptive_book_of_field_grown,_own_root_roses_for_the_people_(1900)#/media/File:Illustrated_and_descriptive_book_of_field_grown,_own_root_roses_for_the_people_(1900)_(20556186605).jpg">Original rose image, public domain on Wikimedia Commons</a>, prior to being cropped and colorized by me.</p>

							</div>

								
